options.modid.autofish.reelInDelay.name: Reel in delay ticks
options.modid.autofish.reelInDelay.descr: Amount of ticks to wait between the fish biting and reeling in the fishing rod.
options.modid.autofish.castDelay.name: Cast delay ticks
options.modid.autofish.castDelay.descrip: Amount of ticks to wait between reeling in the fishing rod and casting it again.
options.modid.autofish.range.name: Range
options.modid.autofish.range.description: The range within the biting fish has to be to reel in the fishing rod.
options.modid.autohighwaybuilder.tunnelW: Sets the width of the tunnel.
options.modid.autohighwaybuilder.tunnelH: Sets the height of the tunnel.
options.modid.autohighwaybuilder.amountO: Sets the amount of blocks to place in a single tick. Setting this value to high may result into ghost blocks.
Sets the amount of blocks to break in a single tick. Setting this value to high may result in weird behaviour.
options.modid.flight.flyingSpeed.name: Speed
options.modid.flight.flyingSpeed.descrip: Sets your flying speed. Setting this value too high may result in getting lagged back.
options.modid.loantikick.amountOfAxisToL: Defines the amount of axis to bind to, the server accepts just the x or z axis, but binding to both is more stable.
options.modid.reach.distance.name: Distance
options.modid.reach.distance.description: Sets the maximum distance you can reach. Setting this value too high may result in ghost blocks.
options.modid.speedmine.speedModifier.de: Sets the value which the mining speed is multiplied by.
options.modid.spider.climbingSpeed.name: Climbing speed
options.modid.spider.climbingSpeed.descr: Sets the speed with which you can climb walls.
options.modid.tp.deltaX.name: Delta X
options.modid.tp.deltaX.description: Sets the relative X coordinate to move.

options.modid.tp.deltaZ.name: Delta Z
options.modid.tp.deltaZ.description: Sets the relative Z coordinate to move.
